Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,engineer, we all want our apps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to look and feel amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We want our code to be flawless,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,our assets to be pixel perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and our store ratings to be five
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,stars nothing less.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's talk about reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As a designer you're focused on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,creating delightful interfaces
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As an engineer you're focused on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,making sure you code works and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result the process becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,slow and everyone feels
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's friction we don't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In the next 10 minutes we're
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,going to look at four things
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:00:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that will really help make
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:00:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The first is using the same
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,terminology.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This saves time, eliminates
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,confusion, and increases
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,credibility with your team and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at some examples of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,how using different terms
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,amongst team members can create
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.83,0:01:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,confusion down the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, pop quiz time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,By a show of hands, which of the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.36,0:01:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,following is the right term for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,this piece of UI -- Is it a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,pop-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Popover? Modal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow you guys are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the right answer is none of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The correct term is UI Alert
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Controller or more currently
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,called an Alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, another show of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of the following is the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,right term for this bar -- Is it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a Header?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Top Tool Bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Navigation Bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:02:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The actual term is Navigation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right and what do we call
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,this bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a Drawer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tool Bar? Bottom Navigation Bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The right term is Tool Bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right last one, show of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of the following is the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,right term for this control?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a Switch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a Toggle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a On-Off Slider?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No? The actual term would be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are just some of the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,elements that have been called
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,different things by different
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure most of you have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced moments where you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,have had a performance stream of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,mental translations when someone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,asks you to implement a Toggle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and the modal trigger a pop-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Adopting mutually understood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,terminology is so important to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,eliminating confusion and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you said cup, when you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,really meant this kind of cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to agree on terminology
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't require additional
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,brain cycles to interpret down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So here are some quick
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,activities that you can try with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,your team to reach that goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take 30 minutes with your team
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,or client to do an app
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,postmortem, just focusing on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it fun, turn it into a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pictionary game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Put things up on a whiteboard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and spend 20 seconds doing flash
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,reactions to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the more formal minded,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,create a report showing all the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,breakdowns due to terminology
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Developer to Apple.com is a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,great resource for referencing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,standard terminology whether in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the Human Interface Guidelines
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or in the API Reference
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Documentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, the second thing I
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,want to talk about is having one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,source of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever been in a situation where
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you've had to pull mockups from
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,a server, stings from a Project
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wiki and then doing like a last
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,minute asset swap send via email
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,or coming back to an old project
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and not knowing which is the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,right version to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashtag designer life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Audience Laughing ]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you and your team or
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,client could agree before hand a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,single place where all of the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,approved deliverables can be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,accessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This would ensure that everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,knows where to go to check out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the necessary assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately designers don't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,have similarly universal options
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,as engineers currently do with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,their IDE's and Version Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an increasing number of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,solutions that have come in the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,last few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So work with your designers to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,find one that integrates with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,their tools and yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thirdly I want to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,talk about having very
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughtful focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an inherent desire to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,start customizing your UI so you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,can stand out from your
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But have you stopped to consider
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the big picture first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When designing and developing an
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,app, you're creating a system
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and systems have a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,complexity where everything is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,interrelated and interdependent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires all of us to think
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,deeply into all the use cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,balancing that against your
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,time, skill, and other system
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,resource constraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It helps if you start from a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,place of familiarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as most of you are more
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,familiar with cooking using a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,non-stick pan, rather than
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,something more specialized like
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a tandoor oven, starting with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,standard patterns and resources
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you get for free in the SDK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,helps to speed up the entire
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,process.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's an example of a standard
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,table.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with a standard table
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,view with this accompanying
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,disclosure indicator accessory,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,would free up time to work on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ensuring that the implementation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This also ensures that the app
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,will work with accessibility
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,features in the OS, which is a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,huge plus for many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when you want to start
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,creating Custom UI, you'll be in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a more empathetic state of mind
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask is it worth the effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are some activities I want
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you to do before going down any
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoroughly consider all the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,intended and etch use cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Write them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Better yet do this together with
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,your team or client.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Find out what resources with the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,OS or your tools that come for
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,free and leverage that as a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,starting point and build
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,accessibility considerations up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,front.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This will ensure even more
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,people can enjoy your app.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right finally I want to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,about show and tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather show more than tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Designers can be guilty of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,throwing static mockups inspects
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,over to engineers, especially in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a time crunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Or engineers can blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,implement the specs without
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,seeking clarification.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when the app is being
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,reviewed by the team, there's
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,invariably complaints from the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,designer that implementation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't match the intent, or
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,frustration from the engineer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that the spec wasn't detailed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to fill in the mental
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,gaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,More often than not,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,demonstrating with a video or a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,small interactive prototype can
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,be extremely valuable in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,communicating the intent or
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,better yet, sparking a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation on constraints,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,possible solutions, and next
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's an example of an
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,animation spec for transitioning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,into a full screen sketch on the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Notes app, the designer could be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,delivering to an engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Showing graphical
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,representations of the curves,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the related parameter value
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,pairs or better yet, the exact
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,API reference, coupled with a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,video of the design animation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,will ensure that the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,implementation will certainly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,match the intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Designers, you can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There are powerful prototyping
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,tools out there like Principle,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Flinto, or even Apple Keynote
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that are really easy to use, so
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I highly encourage you to try
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you want to gain extra
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,credit ability of the engineer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,try using Xcode.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,See how engineers use it to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,bring your designs to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Diving in doesn't even require
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,any coding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can open Xcode, select any
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,app option, track your assets
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,into the asset catalog to see
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for example how your app icons
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,will be implemented.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Or try the storyboard feature to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,create simple flows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hint -- you can import your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,static mockups in here to create
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,interactive prototypes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the object liability to see
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,how built in controls work and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,what they're really called.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And look at all these states and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,properties for the table view
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,accessory that UI Kit is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,providing for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the same tool helps build
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,empathy, keeps you informed, and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,thereby build credibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It can also initiate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,conversations that can be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,helpful to improving the app
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're both working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So here are some activities I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,want you to try with your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Set short face-to-face times and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,run through your prototypes with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that time to tweak values or
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,use the opportunity to explore
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,alternatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And schedule feedback sessions
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,while you're in context.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, grab your designer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or engineer teammate while your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,project is still open and before
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you're about to check in your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:08:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick timely communication
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,reduces errors and mitigates
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,potentially bad situations down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the road when your app is in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,your users hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So in summary, here are the four
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,things to start working on --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,agree on the same terminology,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,decide on a single source where
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone knows where to post and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,check out deliverables, have a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughtful focus on use cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,resource capabilities and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,accessibility and demonstrating
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with dynamic prototypes rather
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,than static screenshots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing these four things will
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,really help with infective
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get clarity on what needs
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to be done and you'll gain
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,credibility with your team,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,client, and users.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
